<wi type="G" value="3498,22,">la muerte</wi>. </t>
</sv>
<sv id="Marcos-9-10">
They kept this saying to themselves, questioning
what the «rising from the dead» meant.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="2532,1,"/><wi type="G" value="2902,4,">Ellos mantuvieron</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,2,"><wi type="G" value="3056,3,">estas palabras</wi></wi>
<wi type="G" value="4314,5,">en</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1438,6,">si mismos</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="4802,7,">cuestionándose</wi>
