<wi type="G" value="4012,9,">alrededor</wi>
<wi type="G" value="846,10,">de ellos</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="2532,11,">y</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1122,12,">escribas</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4802,13,"><wi type="G" value="846,14,">cuestionándolos</wi></wi>. </t>
</sv>
<sv id="Marcos-9-15">
Immediately all the multitude, when they saw
him, were greatly amazed, and running to him greeted him.
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="2532,1,"/><wi type="G" value="2112,2,">Tan pronto</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3956,3,">toda</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,4,"><wi type="G" value="3793,5,">la gente</wi></wi>
<wi type="G" value="846,7,">lo</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1492,6,">vio</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1568,8,">quedaron asombrados</wi>,
<wi type="G" value="2532,9,">y</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4370,10,">corrieron</wi>
a <wi type="G" value="782,11,"><wi type="G" value="846,12,">saludarlo</wi></wi>. </t>
</sv>
<sv id="Marcos-9-16">
He asked the scribes,
<t xml:lang="es"><wi type="G" value="2532,1,"/><wi type="G" value="1905,2,">Él preguntó</wi> a
<wi type="G" value="3588,3,"><wi type="G" value="1122,4,">los escribas</wi></wi>, </t>
<fr>«What are you asking them?»
